These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: western, adventure, zombie, sports
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Movie-Genre:zombie##1
2. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Movie-Genre:sports is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | adventure | sports | zombie |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Pet: goldfish, rabbit, snake, fish
Nationality: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. Pet:rabbit is on the left of Pet:fish##1
2. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:french == Pet:goldfish##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
6. Nationality:french == Pet:goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Pet   | snake | goldfish  | rabbit  | fish |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
City: hamburg, paris, nizza, miami
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of City:miami##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. City:miami is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. City:miami is on the right of City:nizza##1
5. City:hamburg is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| City   | nizza        | miami     | hamburg | paris |

