4. Beverage:7up is on the right of Pet:guinea-pig##1
5. Beverage:juice is between Beverage:7up and Beverage:fanta##2
6. Pet:fish is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:fish is between Beverage:juice and Pet:goat##2
8. Beverage:juice is on the left or right of Beverage:fanta##3

