.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Movie-Genre: scientific, satire, epic, action
Transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. Movie-Genre:satire is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left or right of Transport:helicopter##3
3. Transport:jet-ski is between Movie-Genre:scientific and Transport:helicopter##2
4. Movie-Genre:satire is on the far left or far right##3
5. Transport:subway is on the right of Movie-Genre:action##1
6. Transport:subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | epic   | action | satire |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 